{"tid":1783701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"德國版《香港人權民主法案》三分鐘入來簽，差3萬個！","createTime":"2019-12-15T05:36:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T15:38:19.000Z","uid":280046,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"f3460eefe25eaa3118e842f4ca7e0e5bbb777a19","tid":1783701,"uid":280046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T05:36:58.000Z","msg":"25號之前要簽到5萬個，唔識德文用google chrome可以google translate，詳情同教學請睇 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1782422/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1782422/page/1</a><br />\n聯署傳送門:<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/content/petitionen/_2019/_09/_23/Petition_99604.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fcontent%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_23%2FPetition_99604.html&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWlGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=3d9337a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/content/petitionen/_2019/_09/_23/Petition_99604.html</a><br />\n大概內容係：<br />\n<br />\n第一部分就係提出連署嘅理據:<br />\n1. 示威者與港鐵乘客於元朗站被襲擊，警察約40分鐘後才到場<br />\n2. 天水圍站一名少女被一班防暴警察抬走時，衣服被扯脫<br />\n3. 警察於執行職務時涉嫌偽造證物及將其放置於示威者背包內<br />\n4. 於示威活動大量拘捕參與人士<br />\n5. 831事件: 警察於太子站打車站內的乘客，並關閉所有出口，禁止傳媒及急救人員進入站內<br />\n<br />\n第二部分就係請願德國政府做出制裁:<br />\n1. 對出口控制群眾設備及非致命武器予香港警方作出調整<br />\n2. 對事件日益嚴重以及在港居住德國人的人身安全表示關注<br />\n3. 派遣官員並協助獨立調查以及監察<br />\n4. 承認示威者受到政治打壓並提供政治庇護<br />\n5. 調整於香港警察相關的協議或有關活動<br />\n6. 發出旅遊警示/凍結香港政府高級官員或其家屬的財產"},{"pid":"404138fce8cc5c79a88795e7f6b06dc3de23875e","tid":1783701,"uid":38494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T05:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/saP0o5y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsaP0o5y.jpg&h=f3916056&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed96a35040383d7bcb6a9d799a593bbc614bf367","tid":1783701,"uid":163447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T05:38:28.000Z","msg":"signed and push"},{"pid":"adcbd8274e6968d